# Carlo Career MCP Bundle

This MCP bundle lets Claude access your career documents, answer questions, search Zurich jobs, and recommend courses.

## Install

1. `cd server && npm install`
2. `node index.js`
3. Zip the repo, rename to `carlo-career.mcpb`.
4. Add to Claude Desktop via MCP Bundles.

## Config

Edit `server/config.json` to set your documents folder and API keys.